data.title: Westfield Center
data.text:
Welcome to the Westfield-Center.Com community web site. Our goal is to provide you with useful information about people, places and events in the Village of Westfield Center. The information provided here is gathered from many sources and does not represent official views or policies of The Village of Westfield Center.

If you are looking for the official Village of Westfield Center site, click here to be directed to that web site.

Living Will and Healthcare Power of Attorney

Need help creating the necessary medical care directives in case you have a medical emergency, contact Joseph E. Doty Attorney At Law for expert legal advice for creating the proper health care documents to meet your needs.

If you are just interested in finding out more about how Ohioâ€™s Advance directives can give you a voice in decisions about your medical care when you are unconscious or too ill to communicate, click here to link to the Cleveland Clinic Advance Directives web site to download a free copy of their 44 page general Healthcare Power of Attorney, Living Will and other end-of-life decision documents in Adobe Acrobat format.

Expert PC Repairs, PC Training & Consulting

Digital Technology Solutions is a registered Microsoft Business Partner providing PC hardware and software solutions to small businesses and home computer users. DTS provides onsite computer support and services for small businesses and residential customers in the Northeast Ohio counties of Medina, Wayne and Summit. They offer quality PC support and service at competitive flat rate prices for all your computer services and computer consulting needs.

DTS also sells custom PC systems, provides PC training built to your specification and offers consulting services on software and hardware purchases.
